Their arrest follows shooting at the Bellville taxi rank where the older man worked as a marshal.The men fled in a taxi and police gave chase. The taxi pulled over and arrested the two suspects.A search of the taxi unearthed two guns a .38 Special and a 9mm Star pistol with a filed of serial number.A case of murder possession of an unlicensed firearm and a prohibited firearm was opened.The suspects will appear in the Bellville Magistrate s Court on Monday